'''天主教托里特教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Toritensis}}）是[[羅馬天主教會|羅馬天主教會]]以[[南蘇丹共和國|南蘇丹共和國]][[托里特|托里特]]為中心的一個[[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教朱巴總教區|朱巴總教區]]。

教區位於該國東南部的[[東赤道省|東赤道省]]，2005年時有596,000名教友，廿三個堂區和六十八名司鐸。教區主教現時[[教座出缺|出缺]]<ref name="Vatican20191212">{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 12.12.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/12/12/191212e.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-12-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191215093308/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/12/12/191212e.html |archivedate=2019-12-15 |language=en |date=2019-12-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-en|帕里德·塔班|Paride Taban}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 07.02.2004 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2004/02/07/0062/00201.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-12-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191215103309/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2004/02/07/0062/00201.html |archivedate=2019-12-15 |language=it |date=2004-02-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1983年5月12日自朱巴總教區升格為教區。<ref name="arch">{{cite web|url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19830502_toritensis.html|title=TORITENSIS*|date=1983-05-02|language=la|publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana|accessdate=2019-07-16|archivedate=2019-07-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190716140654/https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19830502_toritensis.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

